00:24:12.099 --> 00:24:13.580
legitimately frightening to me.

00:24:13.580 --> 00:24:15.590
So I was legitimately afraid walking in,

00:24:15.590 --> 00:24:18.550
and what I was surprised
by in the working class

00:24:18.550 --> 00:24:21.550
black community was how nourishing it felt

00:24:21.550 --> 00:24:26.550
to have this posture of confronting

00:24:26.630 --> 00:24:28.190
the system that makes me feel afraid

00:24:28.190 --> 00:24:30.000
walking around like that all the time.

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:33.220
Right, and I think that's what that

00:24:33.220 --> 00:24:35.226
