about the effectiveness

00:24:37.180 --> 00:24:38.800
of that protest, you can say what you want

00:24:38.800 --> 00:24:42.000
about the positivity of guns being out

00:24:42.000 --> 00:24:45.490
in public at all, but it was

00:24:45.490 --> 00:24:47.880
absolutely striking to me
how personally, and also

00:24:47.880 --> 00:24:51.450
in the community, that posture felt like

00:24:53.508 --> 00:24:56.537
a deeply nourishing counterpoint to

00:24:56.537 --> 00:24:59.170
the sort of pressure and persecution

00:24:59.170 --> 00:25:02.060
